{"tid":1569264,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[被秋後] 工程界幾時有自己既工會？","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T00:51:33.000Z","uid":81573,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b13eab4106e83d447ec97b8561099148416615f8","tid":1569264,"uid":81573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:23:30.000Z","msg":"【代朋友post】<br />\n事源831當日九龍灣站都被封<br />\n更有片段係影到有黑警入左站追人追到推跌左個女人 （我搵唔返段片）<br />\n然後有員工就send email比HR<br />\n表示地鐵很危險喎，可唔可以特別工作安排/home office呀？<br />\n<br />\nHR好快咁星期日夜晚覆左：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o1o3QBT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo1o3QBT.jpg&h=c9885e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而最後HR竟然話因為9/2唔似之前咁塞車返唔到工 所以要自己請假<br />\n利申：我當日真係home office, 但都要被請假<br />\n真係一試就知咩係真小人，咩係偽君子<br />\n<br />\n終結：<br />\n希望大家真係要成立工會，啲公司冇野驚，最驚員工團結<br />\n如果佢知道你一人既行動會令其他員工跟隨，去所謂搞事，煩到佢，咁佢就會留意<br />\n而工會係一個最正當既渠道去比大家聯絡、討論、維護員工權益<br />\n雖然我都覺得香港人奴性太重，全民罷工係廢既，但至少參與工會發動既罷工係名正言順，亦有法律基礎<br />\n<br />\n金融業都成立左工會：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/117869569593903?substory_index=0&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107457800635080%2Fposts%2F117869569593903%3Fsubstory_index%3D0%26sfns%3Dmo&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wQHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=08c688de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/117869569593903?substory_index=0&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"22aa733ecbcd5516e006763b98bde8aac4673fb6","tid":1569264,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:23:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"